board.com/uedih.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Edih</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/20/01 2:34:03 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=202.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> pvp ? not use mouse look</span><hr size=1> well i just can't train myself to use the mouse/mouselook to do a circle strafe.<br>anyway to bind the right mouse key to keyboard in game so i can use the keyboard all the way ?<br><br>or i really have to train myself to use the mouse?<br><br> <p><DIV ID="divSign1"><FONT COLOR="#336699"><B>Edih - Povar</B></FONT><BR><FONT COLOR="#33CC99">~~~~</FONT><BR><FONT COLOR="#0099FF"><I>I will sneak into your heart.</I></FONT></DIV></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usilaena.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Silaena</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/20/01 2:38:45 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=202.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Just do as you like ..</span><hr size=1> You dont have to use the mouse look, but it is certainly a big advantage when you master it.. Dont expect to bs all the way, but you will become very harder to hit and faster to be in back of your opponnent. <br><br>I had a twink monk 4 lvl above me with my lil 10 alt magicianne on Rallos that tried to pk me, it seems that he didnt used the mouse look, and let me tell you that I escaped easily from him thanks to my rogue habit .. <br><br>Silaena ShadeClaws 41th Teir'dal Rogue on Tallon Zek <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon2.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ufricka.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fricka</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.thegamevine.com/~Elegant_Rogue/shanks/teenyknot.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/20/01 10:46:37 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=202.topic&index=2>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.thegamevine.com/~Elegant_Rogue/Sigs/4FrickaNEWlt.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Just do as you like ..</span><hr size=1> Mouse look is really a necessity in my opinion, give it one more practice try.<br><br>As for binding the right mouse button I don't think there is an in game way to do do it but you might be able to do it through outside software or other means. <p><table border=0 align=left width=100%>    <tr>      <td width=1><img src="http://www.thegamevine.com/~Elegant_Rogue/Sigs/9frickaface.gif"></td>    <td><font color=FF0000><b><font size=5 face=Times New Roman, Times, serif>Fricka</font></b>       of the Vallon Zek <a href="http://talonguard.org/shanks/index.html">Shanks</a>, Safehouse Ring Warden<br><i><b>Fricka curtsies elegantly...while picking your pocket.</b></i><br></font><a href="http://www.geocities.com/fricka_on_vallon_zek/index.html"><font size=1>Fricka's Sig Gallery</font></a></td></tr></table></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uiamwotan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>I am Wotan</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.thegamevine.com/~Wotan_Rogue/yinyang.gif border=0 BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/20/01 12:46:45 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=202.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.thegamevine.com/~Wotan_Rogue/mask2a.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Just do as you like ..</span><hr size=1> I agree that mouselook is the way to go.  More fun besides as it feels sort of intuitive.  <br><br>However being able to use keyboard control with 3rd person view can be <b>very</b> useful in some situations:<br>- Viewing pursuers while running<br>- fighting while looking about for enemies waiting to jump you<br>- getting slightly ahead of your opponent while chasing in order to prevent "target out of range".<br><br> <p><font size=5 color="gray"><b>Wotan</b><font size=3> Shaman Elder of the <a href="http://www.talonguard.org/shanks"><font color="red">Shanks</font></a> <br><font size=2><b><i>It is better to have less thunder in the mouth and more lightning in the hand.  - Apache Proverb</font></font></font></i></b></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utamerlane.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tamerlane</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/21/01 4:25:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=202.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Just do as you like ..</span><hr size=1> Find what you like to do and do it. <br><br>I don't mouselook. Tried it, didn't like it, never went back. I still do damn good in PvP without it. Experiment. Find what you like and use it.<br><br>-Tamerlain <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umaximilean.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Maximilean</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/21/01 8:38:26 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=202.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Mouselook</span><hr size=1> This was a subject of discussion on a lot of old FPS games, how to control things... Descent in particular, with all the different directions.  <br><br>In my _humble_ opinion (Really humble; my Rogue is on a bluebie server, although he has dueled) for a rogue it's pretty much required, if the other person is in other respects equal to you.  The movements take less time, regardless of how quickly you execute them.  If you're better than them enough to keep them out of position with the keyboard, fine, but what you can do with a single fluid motion with a mouse require a couple of deftly executed keystrokes.<br><br>In my position, when I get around for a backstab in a duel in the middle of melee combat, it's always JUST in time, except for the lucky dodo backs you get from time to time.  With keystrokes, I'd never be landing the close ones.  Someone better with the keys might, I can't say.<br><br>If you still haven't decided, a simple way to practice short of dueling with friends is to rotate around a fixed object, say a cactus or something, at an even distance.<br><br>Also, mouselook is, to my knowledge, required for strafe running, unless I'm missing a key combination.  This is a big help in duels.<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukambic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kambic</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.13thshadowcompany.com/svimages/new_post.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/21/01 11:25:21 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=202.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Mouselook</span><hr size=1> I've tried mouselook, but after years of playing Quake, it is so primitive that I never fully mastered it. That is not to say I can't CoD, I just don't use the mouse. It is too cumbersome in my personal opinion... if you can master it, then great because I am sure it will help you, but I wouldn't say it's necessary. Generally you will either be 1) jousting with a melee or 2) getting nuked from afar by a caster... it only helps so much in either of those cases.<br><br>Quite possibly I was never satisfied with the results because I am on a measly 26.4k connection so with lag factored in a saw no worthwhile difference. Thus, all of the above may be skewed knowledge.<br><br><br> <p><center><hr width=110 color="red"><hr width=210 color="red"><b>Canbik Virulentus</b><br><font size=-1>35<sup>th</sup> Rogue Warden of Rallos Zek</br>Last Knight of Silent Decree<br></font><hr width=210 color="red"><hr width=110 color="red"></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=elegance>Elegance</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/27/01 2:23:08 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=202.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Mouselook</span><hr size=1> its your connection.<br>I cant believe you played quake without the mouse.<br>I would NOT suggest you try tribes if you have a problem with useing your mouse for primary control. <p>Diabalein Avidya <br> One Extra Large Can O Grade A Retarded Whoop Ass<br>Rogue of the 28th thingymajigger<br>118 points of Loving, Hand delivered on the end of a sharp stick</p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showPrevMessage?topicID=202.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showNextMessage?topicID=202.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=202.topic&index=7><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.emailToFriend?topicID=202.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.threadControl?topicID=202.topic><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/dagger.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=202.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm15.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=202.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion">Main Lounge<option value="thesafehousecontractsbountiesjobsquestsetc">News Bulletin<option value="thesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies">Training Studio<option value="thesafehousethebackroomsecret